victron-ve-direct (1.0.0+202606291200-1) stable; urgency=low

  * Initial release.
  * VE.Direct text-protocol parser with checksum validation.
  * JSON broadcast over TCP with SI-scaled fields and enum name decoding.
  * Auto-reconnect on USB disconnect.
  * Supports SmartSolar/BlueSolar MPPT, BMV-700/702/712, Phoenix Inverter.

